exceptions.exn: In environment X : Type m : X -> X -> X u : X n : nat f : nat -> X IHn : ∑ n f = fold_right m u (map f (list_an 0 n)) Unable to unify "∑ n f = fold_right m u (map f (list_an 0 n))" with "∑ n (fun n : nat => f (S n)) = fold_right m u (map f (list_an 1 n))".

original: induction n. - simpl. reflexivity. - simpl. f_equal. apply IHn.
